±In memory of
David Stanley Howard
1971 - 2021
Devoted family man, music lover, raconteur and friend
"Captured my heart, captured my memory, captured a time for me,
I could see a time for me was gonna be, deep in my heart, deep in my memory"
Remembered with Love and a smile. We miss you always Dave."Ì
